des: Nash Icon is the mainstream country format that features a current-based music mix with a superstar library based in the late 80s, 90s and early 2000s. Nash Icon is patterned after WSM-FM in Nashville where it has become the most listened to country station. WILE-AM 1270, 107.9 in Cambridge, OH and 98.5 in Zanesville, OH is locally owned and operated by AVC Communications, Inc.
